products.name: Samsung Galaxy Watch 6
products.description: The image shows a close-up of a black Samsung Galaxy Watch 6 smartwatch. The watch has a green watch face with white text and markings. The watch has a black bezel and a black strap.

products.name: White headphones
products.description: The image shows a pair of white headphones on a gray background. The headphones appear to be over-ear headphones, with a headband and two ear cups. The ear cups are round and white, and the headband is also white. There is a black stripe that goes around the headband and ear cups. The headphones are resting flat on the gray background.

products.name: Silver tablet computer
products.description: The image shows a silver tablet computer with a black front bezel and a large touchscreen display. The back of the tablet is made of aluminum and has an Apple logo in the center. The tablet is resting on a gray background. While I can't definitively say from the image that this is an iPad, it closely resembles an iPad (9th generation), iPad, or Apple iPad 9th Gen.

products.name: Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera 6K
products.description: The image shows a Blackmagic Pocket Cinema Camera 6K. It is a black colored, super 35mm sensor digital film camera with an EF lens mount on the front. The camera has a multifunction handgrip on the right side and a large LCD screen on the back. There are various buttons and dials on the body of the camera.

products.name: Black earbuds
products.description: The image shows a pair of black earbuds on a gray background. The earbuds appear to be wireless, with no wires connecting them to each other or to a device. The earbuds have a round, in-ear design. They have a black charging case in the background.

products.name: Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5
products.description: The image shows the back of a Samsung Galaxy Z Fold5 smartphone. The phone is folded shut, with the hinge visible in the center. The back of the phone is silver and made of glass. There is a triple-lens camera system in the upper left corner, along with an LED flash. The Samsung logo is centered on the back of the phone.

products.name: Apple Watch Series 9 GPS 41mm Starlight Aluminium

products.description: The Apple Watch Series 9 features advanced health monitoring, fitness tracking, and seamless connectivity with your other Apple devices. The 41mm Starlight Aluminium case offers a sleek and stylish design.
